item.title: By: lode
item.dc:creator: lode
item.description:
I had the same error.Resolved by: window->preferences->Arduino->Arduino
check: Use Arduino IDE tools in Eclipse
Then it uploads without a problem!
item.content:encoded:
I had the same error.Resolved by:
window->preferences->Arduino->Arduino

check: Use Arduino IDE tools in Eclipse

Then it uploads without a problem!
